1. Create maven project
2. Import maven dependencies
3. Setup global variables
	- .properties file
	- base class (initialize browser driver)
4. Pageobjects
5. Data providers
6. Convert to TestNG
7. Prepare maven
	- Add surefire plugin
	- cmd run mvn compile
8. log4j
	- make log4j2 xml
	- resource filtering in pom.xml
	- create log file
9. Create listeners (play around)
	- listeners > source > override
	- initialize screenshotter at base.java
	- needs apache commons io package
10. Extent Reports
	- needs extentreports package
	- flush on finish
11. fix parallel execution
	- threadlocal
12. pageobjects optimization
13. jenkins


=== Cucumber ===
14. add features, stepDefinition, cucumberOptions to src test
15. populate .features
16. run testrunner to get stepdefinition template
Tips:
	- use jenkins parameter
	- java oop technique private variables & public methods coding standard
	- use dynamic paths
	- consider running browsers in headless mode
	- static vs non static variables
	- practice multiple tests in one browser initialization 